column2: SELECT p.objID, p.petroRad_u, p.petroRad_g, p.petroRad_r, p.petroRad_i, p.petroRad_z s.objid, s.mjd, s.plate, s.fiberID, sub.mjd, sub.plate, sub.fiberID, sub.SeqNum FROM PhotoObjAll AS p JOIN SpecObjAll AS s JOIN subset as sub ON sub.mjd = s.mjd AND sub.plate = s.plate AND sub.fiberID = s.fiberID AND s.objID = p.objID
